::Amperion::
       He begins swaying again to the rhythm of his chant.  He continues to 
sway as he rises to his feet and follows Kup inside.  He wonders over towards 
the medical ward instinctively and climbs into a CR chamber.  "I've got 
Amperion, lallseday."  He mutters as the door closes on him.

--part1_158.14dde4cc.2ac642b1_boundary
